    { "name": "Queen of Pentacles", "image": "queen_of_pentacles.jpeg", "meaning": "Nurturing, practicality, and abundance.", "fortune": "The queen walks through the forest with ease, her touch bringing life to all she encounters. Her practical nature sees through illusions, bringing abundance where it’s needed most." },
